                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321018-74-victim733 t18321018-74-viclabel415"></join>. On a Sunday, about a month ago, I was in <placeName id="t18321018-74-crimeloc416">Williams'-mews, Margaret-street, St. Pancras</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18321018-74-crimeloc416" type="placeName" value="Williams'-mews, Margaret-street, St. Pancras"></interp>
