                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321018-74-off413 t18321018-74-crimeloc416"></join>; I gave Mrs. Buy a sovereign, to take 1s. 6d. for the stand of a horse - she said she had not change; the prisoner, who stood just behind her, said,"Mistress, I can get change at the tap;" he took the sovereign from her, and did not return.</p>
