                  </persName>
            . (Police-constable S 125.) The prisoner was given to me; I asked him how he came to absent himself with the sovereign - he gave me no other reason but that he was silly; he said he bought a coat for 1s. 6d., and a shirt for 1s., and spent some of the money in getting tipsy, and he had been robbed of the rest.</p>
